│ condition is implied. I will modify this routine to avoid folding when any user is a ReturnInst in a block with multiple predecessors, or more generally, when the parent block of the    │
│ intrinsic has multiple predecessors. This conservative guard prevents miscompilation on non-dedicated exits while preserving correct simplifications elsewhere.                           │
